OL,3,CDomestic abuse charity calls for more
OL,4,Csupport saying system is 'broken'
OL,6,FA domestic abuse charity has called
OL,7,Ffor more support for survivors of
OL,8,Fabuse, saying the system is "broken"
OL,9,Fand unable to cope with the number of
OL,10,Fpeople coming forward.
OL,12,FFearFree, which has bases in Wiltshire
OL,13,Fand Exeter, said it received 4,359
OL,14,Fvictim referrals across the southwest
OL,15,Fin the first six months of the year.
OL,17,FThe charity also said each month it
OL,18,Freceived around 900 calls to the
OL,19,Fhelpline.
