OL,3,CDomestic abuse charity calls for more
OL,4,Csupport saying system is 'broken'
OL,6,F"I think it is a difficult time at the
OL,7,Fmoment in the world and obviously that
OL,8,Fcontributes to escalations in
OL,9,Fviolence," Claire Marshall, CEO of
OL,10,FFearFree, said.
OL,12,F"But there is a very, very strong line
OL,13,Fbetween what is normal factitiousness
OL,14,Fin relationships and abuse, and it's
OL,15,Freally important if people have
OL,16,Fconcerns or find it difficult to
OL,17,Faccept what they're experiencing to
OL,18,Freach out and get help."
