OL,3,CDomestic abuse charity calls for more
OL,4,Csupport saying system is 'broken'
OL,6,FEarlier this month, it was announced
OL,7,Fdomestic abuse specialists will be
OL,8,Fintroduced in 999 control rooms in
OL,9,FEngland and Wales as part of the
OL,10,Fgovernment's pledge to halve violence
OL,11,Fagainst women and girls in a decade.
OL,13,FThe government also announced a new
OL,14,Fdomestic abuse protection order pilot
OL,15,Fthat will order more abusers to stay
OL,16,Faway from victims and impose tougher
OL,17,Fsanctions if they fail to do so.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
