OL,6,FThe plans are part of 'Raneem's Law'
OL,7,Fwhich looks to better protect domestic
OL,8,Fabuse survivors and support police
OL,9,Fefforts to combat violence against
OL,10,Fwomen and girls.
OL,12,FWhile Ms Marshall welcomed the new
OL,13,Flegislation, she said "great
OL,14,Fstrategies are meaningless without the
OL,15,Fresources to actually make those
OL,16,Fthings happen."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
