OL,3,CDomestic abuse charity calls for more
OL,4,Csupport saying system is 'broken'
OL,6,F"The difficulty is that domestic abuse
OL,7,Fcharities, social care, the police,
OL,8,Fthe criminal justice system, are all
OL,9,Fbroken with the sheer volume that's
OL,10,Fcoming at us," she said.
OL,12,FMs Marshall added: "All of those
OL,13,Fsystems need a huge amount of funding
OL,14,Fin order to be able to work and to
OL,15,Fsupport victims and their families
OL,16,Fproperly."
OL,18,FFearFree has provided support to those
OL,19,Fimpacted by domestic abuse, sexual
OL,20,Fviolence and stalking and harassment
OL,21,Ffor more than 30 years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
