OL,4,Csupport saying system is 'broken'
OL,6,FMs Marshall said one of the most
OL,7,Fdifficult things about domestic abuse
OL,8,Fand sexual violence is spotting the
OL,9,Fsigns of abuse.
OL,11,F"It isn't just violence which is
OL,12,Ftypically what people think of as
OL,13,Fdomestic abuse," she explained.
OL,15,F"It can be controlling behaviour, for
OL,16,Fexample controlling someone's
OL,17,Ffinances, who someone sees, whether
OL,18,Fthey're working or not or where
OL,19,Fthey're travelling to.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
